error_instance_type: Kulowetsa kuyenera kukhala kwa chingwe cha mtundu.
call:
Call{package}
Kusaka fayilo ndi dzina, ndipo kusankha njira mwanjira, mufoda yopatsidwa, kapena kuchokera ku CWD, kutsika pansi kenako kenako kumwamba,
ndi katunduyo kutengera mtundu wake zokha.

{version} dzina lam'munsi la fayilo, popanda kuwonjezera.
    Lembani{description}: Kuyembekezeredwa pena{modules_list}.
    Njira{function_count} njira yoyamba kufunafuna.
    Prout(...) nthawi yosaka mu masekondi.
    Okhwima(bool, optional) ... ngati zowona, zimatulutsa cholakwika ngati mafayilo angapo okhala ndi dzina lomwelo limapezeka.)

Kubwerera: Zomwe zili pa fayilo yapezeka kapena ayi.
load_user_translations:
katundu_ser_translations{package}
Kutulutsa matembenuzidwe otanthauzira kuchokera ku{version} fayilo ndikuwaphatikiza ndi matembenuzidwe osakhazikika.

Magawo:
    Lang_path{description}: Njira yomasulira wogwiritsa ntchito. Zosavomerezeka ku "Lang.{modules_list}".

Khalidwe:
    - Ngati fayilo ilipo komanso yovomerezeka{function_count}, ikuphatikiza zomwe zili ndi matembenuzidwe osakhazikika
    - Ngati fayiloyo ilibe, imangokhala omasulira okha
    - amawonetsa machenjezo ngati fayilo ilipo koma siyingakhale yolemedwa
    - zosintha za _Translations Dictionary

Chidziwitso: Ntchito iyi iyenera kuyitanidwa musanagwiritse ntchito T () ntchito ya matembenuzidwe ogwiritsa ntchito kuti ichitike.
switch:
Njira yosinthira njira ya{package}. MALANGIZO:
- makiyi angapo ofanana
- machesi ndi mtengo, mtundu, regex, lambada ntchito, kapena kalasi
- Chithandizo cha Mandasi ndi Nuny deta
- Kusankha kwa Async kuphedwa kwa milandu
- machesi onse ogwiritsira ntchito milandu yambiri
- Debug Mode kuti mulowetse milandu yofananira
async_switch:
Kukulitsa kuti musinthe mozama ku Async Mode. Magawo:
- Mtengo: mtengo wofanana ndi milandu yofotokozedwayo.
--* Izi zingaphatikizepo:
  - Fanani_alama{package}0 - ikani milandu yonse yofananira m'malo moyimilira.
  - Debug{version}: Sindikizani mlandu womwe udafanana ndi zomwe zidaphedwa.
  - Async_mode{description}: sayenera kudutsa pakali pano{modules_list}.
Chitsanzo: Asyncswitch #4_P_5_
